[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10689] changed Type::Float => SyntaxShape::Number to SyntaxShape::Float
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10685] changed a canonicalize test to use a more deeply rooted folder
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10678] renamed nushell's cp command to cp-old making coreutils the default cp
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10686] added Ellie to the standard library
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10675] added Direnv to integrations
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10620] added examples with 
``..``
 and 
``/``
 to 
``path join``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10342] removed 
``random decimal``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10341] removed 
``into decimal``
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10642] fixed parsing of signature inp/out types in predecls
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10637] fixed wrong parsing of signatures in predecl scan
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10683] added a stub 
``dfr``
 command
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10672] updated 
``polars``
 to 
``0.33``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10629] relaxed type-check of key-less 
``table``
/
``record``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9740] fixed output types of 
``math``
 commands to be narrower
Hofer-Julian 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10660] deprecated 
``to xml --pretty {int}``
 in favor of 
``--indent {int}``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10645] added long options for formats
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10641] added long options for filters
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10622] let 
``run_in_login_mode``
 succeed even with broken local config
lavafroth 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10705] moved the 
``partial_from``
 function to the single place it is invoked
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10658] preserved relative paths for local files
quat1024 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10680] updated string casing to use 
``heck``
 (again)
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10659] fixed clippy
CAD97 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10652] fixed clippy in registry_query.rs
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10648] fixed registry query flag validation
bobhy 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10706] fixed dirs to update current ring slot before leaving it
gaetschwartz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10639] improved an error message
DanyPDev 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10623] added themes to help command when available #10318
brunerm99 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10589] improved the error if required field of 
``url join``
 is invalid
zhiburt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10580] fixed a truncation issue in the 
``explore``
 expanded view
